{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Welcome to <strong>Re-Exit</strong>, a psychological horror, spot the anomaly game that challenges your perception and attention to detail. Trapped in a temporal loop caused by an unexplained anomaly, your mission is to observe your surroundings carefully and report any irregularities to find a way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay Overview:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Anomaly Detection:</strong> Each time the elevator doors open, scrutinize the corridor for any changes. Anomalies can be <strong>subtle</strong> or <strong>overt</strong>, testing your observational skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/GrvityShft600.gif?t=1736957952\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzles:</strong> Solve puzzles that test your logic and observation skills</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/StatuePuzz600.gif?t=1736957952\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Threats and Traps:</strong> Encounter deadly enemies and  traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/ZombieShoot600.gif?t=1736957952\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Break the Loop:</strong> Successfully identify anomalies eight times in a row to  realign the distortions and escape the loop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/AnomalyReport.png?t=1736957952\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Estimated Playtime:\u00a0</strong>Approximately 3-4 hours, to discover and experience all anomalies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Can you trust your senses enough to escape the loop?<br><br>Developer's Note:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Re-Exit</i> is developed by a solo indie developer. Your support and feedback are highly appreciated and will help in refining the game further.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736957952","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/page.bg.jpg?t=1736957952","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/f2fe403d4b39d188df55b372d744ed82c9b6977b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736957952","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/f2fe403d4b39d188df55b372d744ed82c9b6977b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736957952","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Welcome to <strong>Re-Exit</strong>, a psychological horror, spot the anomaly game that challenges your perception and attention to detail. Trapped in a temporal loop caused by an unexplained anomaly, your mission is to observe your surroundings carefully and report any irregularities to find a way out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Gameplay Overview:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Anomaly Detection:</strong> Each time the elevator doors open, scrutinize the corridor for any changes. Anomalies can be <strong>subtle</strong> or <strong>overt</strong>, testing your observational skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318470/extras/GrvityShft600.gif?t=1736957952\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzles:</strong> Solve